text: Mariam Cunningham (born 23 November 1951) is a Peruvian equestrian. She competed in the individual dressage event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Peruvian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Peru Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1983 Pan American Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
